text: İdmangücü was established in 1924 in Trabzon, Turkey. It is a sports club and its colours are green and white. Nowadays, İdmangücü is active on football, basketball, handball and swimming branches. Football is the most successful branch of the club and they won many championships in Trabzon before national tournament started. Today, soccer team plays at local amateur league. The head of the club is Tayfun Bircan and their soccer coach is Şükrü Buyukluoğlu. ==References== Category:Sports clubs in Turkey
